Package: nmgc
Type: Package
Title: Nested Multivariate Group Comparisons in R
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Raphael Scherrer
Maintainer: The package maintainer <r.scherrer@evobio.eu>
Description: This package provides tools to facilitate multivariate group comparison analyses in nested datasets where analyses must be replicated within several subsets of the data. Analysis of variance-like tests are used as well as machine learning classification procedures, together with extra tools for assumption testing, dimensionality reduction and plotting.
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
